title: Angels win 2-1 to prevent Rangers from clinching AL West
text:
> Texas Angels win 2-1 to prevent Rangers from clinching AL West Los Angeles Angels shortstop Erick Aybar (2) tries to turn a double play as Texas Rangers Adrian Beltre slides into second base during the sixth inning of a baseball game in Arlington, Texas, Friday, Oct. 2, 2015. Rangers Mitch Moreland was safe at first base. (AP Photo/LM Otero)
